Maryjane Orji Maryjane Orji has emerged winner of the maiden edition of The Beauty Ambassadors Contest. The online monthly contest, aimed at appreciating the beauty of the black woman through a periodic photogenic contest, was organised by Melanin Pride Concept Limited, owners of the Black and Beautiful Group (BBG). The BBG is a platform dedicated to informing, inspiring and celebrating the black woman and her numerous achievements in various spheres. Winners of the contest, which was held in April, were chosen by registered voters on the companyâ€™s website. Focused towards eradicating the notion that the black woman is weak, intimidated and helpless, the BBG platform is designed to challenge the prevailing stereotype, promote a powerful global image of the black woman and share culture.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .